{"title": "Výlet do Pluta", "content": "<div><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">Vím, že jednou ke mně vkročí</span></em></span><br style=\"color:#27292b;text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">cosi tiše za šera.</span></em></span></div><div><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\">Stín se krčí. Pak znenáhla se mihne.</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\">Duhovka mi zjihne.</span><br style=\"color:#27292b;text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">Vítězně se zadívá v mé oči</span></em></span><br style=\"color:#27292b;text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">sfinga či snad chiméra.</span></em></span></div>", "published": "2017-08-07T21:21:00Z", "tags": [], "filename": "/2017/08/vylet-do-pluta.html"}